{
  "stem": "26731.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would the Ru-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] quite decently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They saw to it that there was enough food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought it in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They actually, for instance, they went to the cemeteries for instance, Jewish cemetery, too, and said, well, you're going to stop growing flowers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The few greenhouses that are still-- some actually survived the bombing, strangely enough-- you are going to, for instance, have tomato plants for the population.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And instead of flowers, you grew beans or something else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And actually we went to a cemetery and picked out the tomato plants, See at-- shortly after the war, we moved out to a, a house, actually, in the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quite difficult because of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there we had the opportunity to grow our own-- we grow-- we had potatoes, and green beans, and tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was quite important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was one of the reasons why we actually moved out there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If you stayed in the city, it was quite difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even there in the parks, they grew vegetables.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Russians encouraged it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But right after the war, of course, we were looking for food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when something else, we said, just-- there are certain neighbors, certain people who harassed us, who are watching whether we really bought our food between 4:00 and 5:00, and whether they would starve us, right.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And just wait, what you're going to do to them when the war is over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now when the war was over, we didn't lower ourselves to go after them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I, I was actually always lucky.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was never beaten up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I actually did not see any physical abuse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes, vocal abuse, but I didn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It has happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
